description: Handheld, delicious goodness on the go is coming your way, thanks to The Pasty Republic! Perfectly formed pastry shells filled with the best meat and veggies around are what you'll find when you try this terrific truck's curbside cuisine. Along with their freshly made salads and tasty ice cream, you're sure to find something that you'll love from The Pasty Republic!
name: The Pasty Republic
